  "title": "Assassins",
  "description": "Stephen Sondheim's Assassins is a bold, chilling, and darkly funny journey through the minds of America's four successful and five would-be presidential assassins. This Tony-Award winning musical explores celebrity culture and the violent means that some will use to obtain the American Dream.",
